      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Yes — EM is a valid Scrabble word in both TWL and SOWPODS. It scores 4 points and refers to a typographic unit of measurement — the width of the capital letter M in a given font. You know it from em-dashes (—) and em-spaces. At 4 points for just 2 tiles, EM is one of the stronger two-letter words thanks to M's 3-point value.</p>

