        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">EM scores <span class="text-white font-medium">exactly double</span> what EN scores (4 vs 2). When you have both E+M and E+N available, EM is always the stronger 2-letter play. The M tile's 3-point value makes EM one of the top-scoring two-letter words in the game.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy: When to Play EM</h2>
