        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">M on premium squares:</span> M is worth 3 points — on a Double Letter that's 6 from one tile, making EM score 7 total. On Triple Letter, M gives 9, and EM scores 10 for just 2 tiles.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
